<p xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/legaldocml/ns/akn/3.0">(Official Journal of the European Union L 124 of 27 April 2004)</p>On page 22, Annex I, point (58) (concerning Article 59(2)):<p xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/legaldocml/ns/akn/3.0"><!--default P | TXT -->for:</p>
<mod xmlns="http://docs.oasis-open.org/legaldocml/ns/akn/3.0">
