      <paragraph>
         <num>&apos;2.</num>
         <content>
            <p>If, over a period of 12 months, an official is absent for up to three days because of sickness for a total of more than 12 days, …&apos;,</p>
         </content>
      </paragraph>
   </quotedStructure>
</mod>
